What is React?
Clinet Side JavaScript library
- Created & maintained by facebook
- Used to build dynamic user interfaces
- "Component" based
- Most popular framework in the industry

React is "technically" a library but is often refered to as a framework as it is used for many of hte same reasons as a framework

Why Learn & User React?
- Build a powerful Frontend/UI
- Code Organization
- Reusable Components
- Speed & performance
- Makes things much easier
- Very popular in the industry
- Look at eadch element as individual Components
- Organized structure
- Logic, output & style
- COmponents can have "props" & "state"